var Matrix4 = function() {

    this._dirty = true;

 * @param  {clay.Matrix2d} m2d
 * @return {clay.Matrix4}
 */
Matrix4.fromMat2d = function(m4, m2d) {
    m4._dirty = true;
    var m2d = m2d.array;
    var m4 = m4.array;
 
    m4[0] = m2d[0];
    m4[4] = m2d[2];
    m4[12] = m2d[4];
 
    m4[1] = m2d[1];
    m4[5] = m2d[3];
    m4[13] = m2d[5];
 
    return m4;
};
